This is a poker game where{nl}
you may exchange cards{nl}
once.{waitkey}{clearbox}At the start, you are{nl}
dealt 5 cards.{waitkey}{clearbox}Use the D-pad to select{nl}
the cards you want to{nl}
keep,{waitkey}{nl}
then press O, X, Triangle,{nl}
or Square to HOLD them.{waitkey}{clearbox}Once you've decided which{nl}
cards to HOLD, press R1{nl}
or R2 to re-draw,{waitkey}{nl}
and the remaining cards{nl}
will be replaced.{waitkey}{clearbox}After the re-draw, if you{nl}
have a winning hand,{nl}
you win.{waitkey}{clearbox}The more coins you bet,{nl}
the higher the payout{nl}
(ODDS) when you win.{waitkey}{clearbox}If you complete a hand,{nl}
you can enter an Extra{nl}
Game wagering that payout.{waitkey}{clearbox}If you don't want to play{nl}
the Extra Game, select{nl}
TAKE SCORE.{waitkey}{clearbox}There are 3 types of{nl}
Extra Games, and the payout{nl}
doubles with each win.{waitkey}{clearbox}By winning the Extra Game{nl}
repeatedly, the payout can{nl}
reach up to 1,000,000 coins.{waitkey}{clearbox}However, if you fail even{nl}
once, your entire payout{nl}
is forfeited — so be{nl}
careful.{waitkey}{clearbox}<Extra Game 1>{nl}
- HI & LOW{waitkey}{clearbox}One face-up card and four{nl}
face-down cards are shown{nl}
on screen.{waitkey}{clearbox}From the four face-down{nl}
cards, pick the one with{nl}
a higher number than the{nl}
face-up card.{waitkey}{clearbox}If the chosen card matches{nl}
the face-up card in value,{nl}
it's a draw and you{nl}
try again.{waitkey}{clearbox}<Extra Game 2>{nl}
- BIG & SMALL{waitkey}{clearbox}One face-up card and one{nl}
face-down card are shown{nl}
on screen.{waitkey}{clearbox}Guess whether the{nl}
face-down card is higher{nl}
or lower than the{nl}
face-up card.{waitkey}{clearbox}If the chosen card matches{nl}
the face-up card in value,{nl}
you lose — so be careful.{waitkey}{clearbox}<Extra Game 3>{nl}
- RED & BLACK{waitkey}{clearbox}One face-down card is{nl}
shown on screen.{waitkey}{clearbox}If you think the face-down{nl}
card is a Heart or Diamond,{nl}
choose RED.{waitkey}{clearbox}If you think it's a Club{nl}
or Spade, choose BLACK.{waitkey}{clearbox}If your chosen color matches{nl}
the card's color,{nl}
you win.{waitkey}{ret}

