This slot machine consists{nl}
of 5 large drums and{nl}
16 small drums.{waitkey}{clearbox}The number of bet coins{nl}
determines how many{nl}
winning lines are active.{waitkey}{clearbox}You can bet up to{nl}
8 coins at a time.{waitkey}{clearbox}Bets 1, 2, 5, 6 use{nl}
horizontal lines; bets{nl}
3, 4, 7, 8 use vertical{nl}
lines as judgment lines.{waitkey}{clearbox}Note: bets 5 through 8{nl}
each have 2 judgment{nl}
lines per bet.{waitkey}{clearbox}When the game starts,{nl}
all large and small drums{nl}
begin spinning.{waitkey}{clearbox}After spinning for a while,{nl}
the small drums stop first{nl}
while the large drums{nl}
keep spinning.{waitkey}{clearbox}Press O, X, Triangle,{nl}
or Square to shift the{nl}
small drums clockwise.{waitkey}{clearbox}Adjust the small drums{nl}
so the symbols are{nl}
more likely to align.{waitkey}{clearbox}Once you're done adjusting{nl}
the small drums, press R1{nl}
or R2 to stop{nl}
the large drum.{waitkey}{clearbox}If 3 or more matching{nl}
symbols line up along{nl}
a bet line, you win.{waitkey}{clearbox}Bets 1-4 can align up{nl}
to 5 symbols; bets 5-8{nl}
can align up to 4.{waitkey}{clearbox}Also, if the large drum's{nl}
symbols align diagonally,{nl}
at all four corners,{nl}
or all at once,{waitkey}{nl}
you win regardless of{nl}
which line was bet.{waitkey}{clearbox}A large drum win multiplies{nl}
the payout by the{nl}
number of coins bet.{waitkey}{ret}

