Each slot machine has{nl}
different symbols that{nl}
tend to hit more often.{waitkey}{clearbox}Rather than sticking{nl}
to one machine, try{nl}
several different ones.{waitkey}{clearbox}Also, it's easy to forget{nl}
about the small drums{nl}
mid-game, so watch out.{waitkey}{nl}
Skillfully adjusting the{nl}
small drums is the secret{nl}
to growing your coins.{waitkey}{clearbox}Betting low might seem safe,{nl}
but you risk big losses{nl}
when it counts.{waitkey}{nl}
It's best to always{nl}
go in with 8-BET{nl}
(full bet).{waitkey}{ret}

