Two dice are rolled on{nl}
screen, and you guess{nl}
their total.{waitkey}{clearbox}You can bet on any of{nl}
the 11 spots from 2 to 12,{nl}
and you can bet on multiple{nl}
spots in one game,{waitkey}{nl}
but the max bet per{nl}
spot is 100.{waitkey}{clearbox}If the dice total matches{nl}
a spot you bet on,{nl}
you win and receive{nl}
a payout based on the odds.{waitkey}{clearbox}You may also wager{nl}
your winnings in an{nl}
Extra Game.{waitkey}{clearbox}In the Extra Game, you{nl}
don't guess the exact total;{nl}
instead,{waitkey}{nl}
any total other than 7{nl}
counts as a win.{waitkey}{nl}
(Payouts vary by total.){waitkey}However, if a 7 is rolled,{nl}
the game ends and all{nl}
your winnings are forfeited,{nl}
so be careful.{waitkey}{ret}

